{"tid":1239879,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"監警會委員全部由行政長官委任","createTime":"2019-06-18T08:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T09:12:55.000Z","uid":179292,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c2cef362ef7ac78e02ead27308ce3f5147b45831","tid":1239879,"uid":179292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:49:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">監佢老母<br />\n監警會=垃圾<br />\n監警會委員全部由行政長官委任</span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0d54ca6b23e4e883e207ae28b1eb6f23643bdf36","tid":1239879,"uid":179292,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點燃投訴警狗呀!!!!</span><br />\n-------------------------------<br />\n監警會是根據《獨立監察警方處理投訴委員會條例》（《監警會條例》）（香港法例第604章）成立的獨立機構，其職能是觀察、監察和覆檢警務處處長就須匯報投訴的處理和調查工作。<br />\n<br />\n監警會由一名主席、三名副主席和不少於八名委員組成。委員全部由行政長官委任，分別來自社會不同界別，包括法律界、醫學界、教育界、社福界、商界和立法會議員等。監警會借助委員多方面的專業知識，獨立、公正、透徹地監察投訴警察課的調查工作。截至2017年3月31日，監警會共有28名委員。<br />\n<br />\n監警會於2009年6月1日成為法定機構。隨著《監警會條例》生效，警方有法定責任遵從監警會根據條例所提出的要求。條例進一步提高監警會的獨立性，以履行其監察職能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/about_us/about_ipcc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout_us%2Fabout_ipcc.html&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAWdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=66fcd90c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/about_us/about_ipcc.html</a>"},{"pid":"63c9b4639ab00582e2ca13e89d8540b956a9d6c1","tid":1239879,"uid":38761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:51:31.000Z","msg":"以前好D，真係會揾D社會賢達，但係宜家當狗餅派！！！"},{"pid":"b05bed1b245547a4df78f9d0563307a657ea1797","tid":1239879,"uid":35205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:52:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190605/59672079\" data-sr-url=\"http